data.description: This exceptional custom home is a true masterpiece, boasting a wealth of upgrades that will leave you breathless. Nestled on a generous half-acre within the highly sought-after LaGrange Shores subdivision, you'll relish in the tranquility of this remarkable locale, all without the restrictions of HOA's. A grand 8' Craftsman front door invites you to step into elegance. The 10' tall foyer adorned with pristine white shiplap walls sets the tone for the impeccable craftsmanship that awaits. To your left, a sophisticated formal dining room awaits, showcasing exquisite wainscoting and an elegant tray ceiling. Enter the heart of the home, an expansive open living area graced by a double tray ceiling that adds an element of luxury. A captivating brick gas fireplace stands as a centerpiece, exuding warmth and charm. French doors beckon you to explore the outdoor oasis that lies beyond. Prepare to be amazed by the kitchen, a culinary dream brought to life. Fantasy Brown Leathered Textured Granite countertops take center stage, perfectly complemented by a 4" x 12" subway tile backsplash that adds a touch of modernity. Illuminating the space, undermount cabinet lighting dances across the Legacy Dovetail, Soft Close white matte shaker style cabinets, and a bespoke Custom Range Hood. The magnificent 10' x 4' island in rich brown hues boasts a deep composite sink, crowned by three stunning glass pendant lights that evoke elegance. Appliances are a testament to quality, featuring Whirlpool's black stainless-steel range proudly crafted in America. A five-burner gas stove, complete with a convenient pot filler, promises culinary excellence. An incredibly quiet dishwasher ensures seamless functionality while maintaining the serenity of the space. Gorgeous wire-brushed Hickory hardwood floors in a rich 6" plank pattern grace every inch of this home, while porcelain tiles of 12" x 24" and 18" x 18" embellish wet areas and the hallway from the garage, ensuring convenience throughout. This home redefines comfort by banishing all carpets. The primary bedroom is a retreat, highlighted by a captivating white shiplap feature wall and an exterior door to the backyard. The ensuite primary bathroom is a haven of luxury with a double-head shower and an oversized soaking tub, both elegantly adorned with ceiling-reaching tiles. Quartz countertops adorn dual sinks, while dual walk-in closets boast custom white wood shelving, a true delight for the organization enthusiast. Functionality meets style in the well-appointed laundry room, complete with a utility sink and built-in laundry hampers. Adjacently positioned to the Primary Bathroom, it caters to convenience. Three additional bedrooms adorned with custom wood shelving and a secondary bathroom boasting twin sinks and a quartz countertop, redefine contemporary living. A convenient powder room is nestled off the mudroom, which ushers you into the 24'6" x 24' garage featuring a resilient resin floor and an accompanying walk-in closet. Every inch of this residence exudes luxury, featuring solid five-panel interior doors, chic custom cordless roman shades, and meticulous custom trim that underscores the home's impeccable attention to detail. Embrace the lifestyle you've always envisioned... schedule your walk through today and experience the pinnacle of refined living! Professional photos coming soon.
